lastCommitMessage: Enhance SellerProductPage with new product creation features and validation improvements
- Implemented default form data initialization for new products, providing a better starting point for sellers.
- Added a quick-fill button to automatically populate required fields in the product form, streamlining the product creation process.
- Enhanced validation logic for both edit and create modes, ensuring comprehensive checks for required fields and providing user feedback for missing or incorrect data.
- Improved image handling to support both new uploads and existing images, maintaining a seamless user experience during product management.
